Softer materials make your weapon suited to knock out instead of kill, and special protrusions let you catch weapons and disarm your foes. 

Your innovation gains the [[Disarm]] and [[Nonlethal]] traits. You can choose whether to apply the nonlethal trait on each attack with your innovation.